text: Manpreet Akhtar (1965 – 18 January 2016) was a Punjabi folk singer and the sister of Dilshad Akhtar, who was also a Punjabi-language folk singer. == References == Category:People from Faridkot district Category:1965 births Category:2016 deaths Category:Indian female folk singers Category:Indian folk singers Category:Singers from Punjab, India Category:20th-century Indian singers Category:20th-century Indian women singers Category:Women musicians from Punjab, India
title: Manpreet Akhtar
